0-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/boygenius-sinead-o-connor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/boygenius-sinead-o-connor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/boygenius-sinead-o-connor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">Boygenius</a>发行了传统爱尔兰民谣“The Parting Glass”的翻唱版，以向已故的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">Sinead O&#39;Connor</a>致敬。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/sinead-oconnor-obituary-3473864">Sinéad O&#39;Connor，1966-2023：一位正直、强烈和诚实的艺术家</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（11 月 17 日），由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">Phoebe Bridgers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julien-baker">Julien Baker</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lucy-dacus">Lucy Dacus</a>组成的三人组合 Boygenius 在流媒体平台上分享了这首歌曲，并与爱尔兰民谣二人组 Ye Vagabonds 合作。这首歌是为了纪念西尼德·奥康纳 (Sinead O&#39;Connor) 而录制并发行的，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">她于 7 月去世，享年 56 岁</a>。</p><p>奥康纳于 2002 年录制并发行了著名的《The Parting Glass》。博伊吉纽斯在社交媒体上写道，该封面将惠及慈善机构，特别是艾斯林项目，该旅行将其描述为“一个与儿童和青少年一起成长的课后项目”。位于爱尔兰都柏林的贫困地区”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CzvDPA4AkUQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: c